VXI/VME Interrupt Event

Inherits from Event class.

Long Name Description
Event Information:Received Interrupt Level Returns the VXI interrupt level on which the interrupt was received. This is valid only for the VXI/VME Interrupt event. Details
Event Information:Interrupt Status ID Returns the 32-bit status/ID retrieved during the IACK cycle. This is valid only for the VXI/VME Interrupt event. Details
Event Information:Event Type Returns the unique logical identifier for the event type of the specified event. Details
